OL,3,CChange rules to allow public sector
OL,4,Cinvestment borrowing, Swinney to tell
OL,5,CReeves
OL,7,FThe UK Government should change the
OL,8,Ffiscal rules to allow borrowing for
OL,9,Fpublic sector investment, Scotland's
OL,10,FFirst Minister is expected to say in a
OL,11,Fspeech on Monday.
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of the Budget on
OL,14,FOctober 30, John Swinney will address
OL,15,Fan audience of academics, think tanks
OL,16,Fand representatives of the public,
OL,17,Fprivate and third sector in Edinburgh.
