OL,5,CReeves
OL,7,F"In the advanced economies of the
OL,8,FOECD, the average amount of public
OL,9,Fsector investment is nearly 4% of GDP
OL,10,Fa year," the First Minister is
OL,11,Fexpected to say.
OL,13,F"These economies are spending nearly
OL,14,F50% more than the UK government spends
OL,15,Fon investment.
OL,17,F"And the consequences are very real
OL,18,Ffor our economy, for our public
OL,19,Fservices, and for UK citizens.
