OL,5,CReeves
OL,7,FThe First Minister will also urge the
OL,8,FGovernment to seek to increase public
OL,9,Fsector investment to at least 3% of
OL,10,FGDP, eventually rising to the OECD
OL,11,Faverage of 3.7%.
OL,13,F"It would mean that governments in all
OL,14,Ffour nations could plan on the basis
OL,15,Fof stable, predictable, funding
OL,16,Farrangements to build the
OL,17,Finfrastructure we all need and which I
OL,18,Fwant to deliver for Scotland," he will
OL,19,Fsay.
