OL,7,FThe First Minister is also expected to
OL,8,Fpush Ms Reeves to increase public
OL,9,Fspending in the October 30 Budget,
OL,10,Fdescribing the past seven years as a
OL,11,F"long, dark economic winter".
OL,13,F"One thing is clear, we have reached a
OL,14,Fturning point, a pivotal moment for UK
OL,15,Fdecision-making in a world of
OL,16,Fsustained turmoil," he will say.
OL,18,F"That is why I believe the United
OL,19,FKingdom faces a make or break moment
OL,20,Fin this next Budget. It must be
OL,21,Fseized."
