OL,7,FA Treasury spokesperson said: "The
OL,8,FChancellor has vowed to lead the most
OL,9,Fpro-growth Treasury in history and has
OL,10,Fbeen clear that it is important that
OL,11,Fwe count the benefits of public
OL,12,Finvestment and not just the cost of it.
OL,14,F"We have already taken action to
OL,15,Fdeliver more investment in the UK
OL,16,Feconomy by fixing the broken planning
OL,17,Fsystem and setting up a new National
OL,18,FWealth Fund, and the International
OL,19,FInvestment Summit secured a record-
OL,20,Fbreaking #63 billion in investment
OL,21,Fcommitments."
